wiki.content:
Song featured in 
 - "A Couch in New York" / "Un divan à New York", a 1996 movie with William Hurt and Juliette Binoche, directed by Chantal Akerman
 - "Bella Martha", a 2002 German movie starring Martina Gedeck, directed by Sandra Nettelbeck
 - "No Reservations", the 2007 remake of the German film, starring Catherine Zeta-Jones, directed by Scott Hicks
 - "French Kiss", a 1995 movie starring Meg Ryan and Kevin Kline, directed by Lawrence Kasdan
